## 12. GENERAL AI CODE QUALITY PATTERNS

### Flaw: Excessive Comments and Documentation

**Description:** AI-generated code contains verbose, redundant comments on nearly every line, increasing cognitive load without adding value.

**Statistics:** Found in 90-100% of AI-generated code (OX Security analysis of 300+ repos).

**Bad Code:**
```rust
// Create a new vector to store the results
let mut results = Vec::new();
// Iterate over each item in the input
for item in items {
    // Check if the item is valid
    if item.is_valid() {
        // Add the valid item to results
        results.push(item);
    }
}
```

**Good Code:**
```rust
let results: Vec<_> = items.into_iter().filter(|item| item.is_valid()).collect();
```

